#### Query Parameters
| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| examId | string | Yes | Filter by exam ID |

#### Example Request
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.analytics.com/v1/classAnalytics/exam1" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer your-token" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

#### Example Response
